<h3>Engine checks</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Oil change – the grade used will depend on the manufacturer’s recommendation</li>
    <li>New oil filter</li>
    <li>New air filter</li>
    <li>New spark plugs</li>
    <li>Test/replace/top-up coolant as required</li>
</ul>

<h3>Road test</h3>

<p>With motorcycle servicing, a full service will include a road test to ensure the motorbike is running as expected.</p>

