<h3>How much is a motorbike service? - How much is a full service for a motorbike?</h3>

<p>The cost of a full motorbike service depends on the size of your engine and the specific pricing of your chosen garage.</p>

<p>Motorcycle servicing costs at an independent garage may be less than motorcycle services costs at a garage which is part of a nationwide or regional chain, because the latter has larger operating costs for things like marketing and city centre business rates. And unlike some small garages, chains will need to pay VAT.</p>

<p>Here is a rough idea of what you might expect to pay for a motorbike service:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Below 250cc: £80 - £130</li>
    <li>250cc – 600cc: £90 - £160</li>
    <li>Up to 1000cc: around £180</li>
</ul>